# Environment Variables for Job Application System

# Serper.dev API Key (Google Search API)
# Sign up: https://serper.dev/
# Cost: $50 for 5000 searches ($0.01 per search)
# Used for: Company tech stack research via Google search
SERPER_API_KEY=your-serper-api-key-here

# GitHub API Token (Optional)
# Create: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Free tier: 5000 requests/hour
# Used for: Researching company GitHub repositories
# GITHUB_TOKEN=your-github-token-here

# Perplexity API Key (Optional)
# Sign up: https://www.perplexity.ai/
# Cost: $0.01-0.05 per query
# Used for: AI-powered company research
# PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=your-perplexity-key-here

# Usage:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in your API keys
# 3. Load in shell: source .env (or export commands)
# 4. For Netlify: Use netlify env:set KEY "value"
